---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { links } from '../data/links';
---
<MainLayout title="Projects | Corrine J Blackthorn">
<section>
<div class="container">
<div class="section-heading">
<span class="kicker">Projects</span>
<h1>Things I'm building.</h1>
<p>These are the projects, businesses, creative endeavors, and initiatives that make up different parts of my work and interests.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid">
<article class="card"><h3>TechNerd</h3><p>Technology consulting, engineering, security, and technical solutions.</p><a class="button" href={links.ventures.techNerd}>Visit</a></article>
<article class="card"><h3>Rootworks</h3><p>Learning, experimentation, infrastructure, and technical exploration.</p><a class="button" href={links.ventures.rootworks}>Visit</a></article>
<article class="card"><h3>Blackthorn Field Notes</h3><p>Essays, reflections, technical writing, and future publications.</p><a class="button" href={links.ventures.blackthornFieldNotes}>Visit</a></article>
<article class="card"><h3>Glass & Thorns</h3><p>Music, art, and creative expression.</p><a class="button" href={links.ventures.glassAndThorns}>Visit</a></article>
<article class="card"><h3>Petals & Frames</h3><p>Photography, visual storytelling, and creative work.</p><a class="button" href={links.ventures.petalAndFrame}>Visit</a></article>
<article class="card"><h3>Blackthorn's Tropicals</h3><p>A growing collection of plants, learning, and cultivation.</p><a class="button" href={links.ventures.blackthornsTropicals}>Visit</a></article>
<article class="card"><h3>Thorns to Roses</h3><p>Advocacy, support, coaching, and transformation.</p><a class="button" href={links.ventures.thornsToRoses}>Visit</a></article>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="quote-band"><div class="container"><blockquote>Blackthorn Enterprises is the business umbrella that helps organize several of these projects. Most people interact with the individual projects directly.</blockquote></div></section>
</MainLayout>